{"tid":2072200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google前CEO：華為幫北京收集情報","createTime":"2020-06-20T12:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T13:47:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9eedc21b3ab839063f46496bab13534e511ae19f","tid":2072200,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:06:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200620/YYMSFA56MCH5LLKZYQQ5KXY5M4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200620%2FYYMSFA56MCH5LLKZYQQ5KXY5M4%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPducwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=39e3a52d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200620%2FYYMSFA56MCH5LLKZYQQ5KXY5M4%2F&h=8d6a181c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200620/YYMSFA56MCH5LLKZYQQ5KXY5M4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nGoogle前CEO：華為幫北京收集情報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GB5EBOABDTBQBIMNLIEENBJMNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGB5EBOABDTBQBIMNLIEENBJMNY.jpg&h=1e7ddfc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施密特相信華為實有扮演中國訊號情報機構角色。<br />\n<br />\n中國網絡設備公司華為近年為多國建設5G網絡，惟外界對設備會否設「後門」為中國收集情報存有疑問。美國國防創新委員會主席施密特（Eric Schmidt）就斷言華為毫無疑問會發送情報予中國，做了在國家安全方面令人無法接受的行為。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：澳遭國家級網攻  中共疑幕後黑手  或因倡查疫源遭報復<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指角色等同「國安局」<br />\n<br />\n65歲的施密特是科企Google的前行政總裁，他接受英媒訪問時指出華為。。。。。無疑問華為的路由器數據最終會落入中國政府控制。<br />\n<br />\n他認為應付華為的方法是以質素一樣好的產品與它競爭，又承認華為的核。。。。。年，情況就如歐洲空中巴士（Airbus）公司多年前努力追趕美國航空業一樣。<br />\n<br />\n在國安憂慮下，英已限制華為只能佔5G設備的35%，不。。。。。指控，強調華為是私企，獨立於任何國家。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"e77833f774b68bac3b6ac65e25a20332b97c3a82","tid":2072200,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/